Description
Experience the fusion of comfort and style with our 3' X 5' small rectangular area rug. Designed with the modern home in mind, this rug showcases an enticing ivory and navy color blend that complements any room setup effortlessly. Expertly power-loomed in Turkey, this rug embodies premium craftsmanship renowned for important quality parameters. It's made from 75% durable polypropylene and 25% shrink polyester, promising long-lasting performance and retaining its fresh look even with high traffic use. The rug has a contemporarily elegant design, featuring a height of 3/8" to provide a plush feel and elegant depth, enriching your living space with an understated yet sophisticated touch. Most importantly, our rug has earned the OEKO-TEX certification, ensuring it's free from harmful substances and safe for your home environment, giving you peace of mind. Add this luxurious, contemporary-style area rug to your d?cor and enjoy an instant update to your indoor space. Affordable, eco-friendly, and elegant - that's what our small rectangle ivory/navy rug delivers!
